    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she's a total dream. This car has been babied since day one\u2014always garage-kept, meticulously cleaned, and it still has that 'new car' feel every time you hop in! It drives like a charm and looks absolutely stunning. I'm sad to see it go, but I'm looking for a great new owner who will appreciate it as much as I have. You really have to see this one in person to believe how pristine it is! Feel free to reach out if you want to chat or come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
