    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been climate-control garage-kept since day one and has never seen a drop of rain. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a professional-grade ceramic coating and zero imperfections, chips, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, the original factory scent lingers, and every electronic component functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is indistinguishable from new, supported by a complete, documented service history from authorized dealerships. It features a spotless undercarriage and brand-new tires. This is a rare opportunity to own a preserved piece of automotive excellence that looks, smells, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. All original manuals, two sets of keys, and a custom car cover are included.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
